12.06.name: wordpress/blue-admin
12.06.description:
This is a simple and clear admin design that makes your WordPress administration section more clear and relaxed. Read more about Blue Admin.

Features

  • Clean and clear admin design.
  • Custom navigation menus to your WordPress Adminbar/Toolbar.(only compatible for WordPress 3.3 or above versions)
  • RTL support for Arabic and other RTL languages.
